        "translations": {
          "en": "Muhammad ibn Ahmad al-Sinani (may God be pleased with him) narrated to us. He said: Muhammad ibn Abi Abdillah al-Asadi al-Kufi narrated to us from Musa ibn 'Imran al-Nakha'i, from his uncle al-Husayn ibn Yazid al-Nawfali, from Ali ibn Salim, from Abu Basir, from Abu Abdillah al-Sadiq (peace be upon him).",
